<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/stmLandUseValue/fAVillage> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "FA-Village are undeveloped gaps in the building land, which can be declared a village area once the legal criteria have been met."@en <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/stmLandUseValue:1> .
<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/stmLandUseValue/trafficAreas> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Traffic areas are those areas which are intended for the handling of moving and stationary traffic, as well as for the development of building land and open land"@en <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/stmLandUseValue:1> .
<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/stmLandUseValue> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#hasTopConcept> <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/stmLandUseValue/fAResidentialArea> <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/stmLandUseValue:1> .
<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/stmLandUseValue/specialUseOpenland> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "sind Flächen, wenn auf Grund ihrer besonderen Standortgunst die flächenhafte Nutzung im Vordergrund steht und diese nicht typischerweise einem Baulandgebiet zuzuordnen ist. Insbesondere sind das Flächen für Erwerbsgärtnereien, Erholungszwecke, Spielzwecke, Parkanlagen, Friedhöfe,…"@de <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/stmLandUseValue:1> .
<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/stmLandUseValue/rAVillage> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "RA-Villages are not fully-fledged building land which, once defects have been remedied, become fully-fledged village areas."@en <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/stmLandUseValue:1> .
<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/stmLandUseValue/rAIndustry> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "RA-Industry"@en <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/stmLandUseValue:1> .
<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/stmLandUseValue/dAResidentialArea> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "DA-Residential areas are not yet fully-fledged residential areas, but their construction is expected and they are not designated as redevelopment areas."@en <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/stmLandUseValue:1> .
